originalSql:
WITH ranked_movies AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id,
        t.title,
        t.production_year,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY t.production_year ORDER BY t.id) AS Ran
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    WHERE 
        t.production_year IS NOT NULL
),
actor_info AS (
    SELECT 
        a.person_id,
        a.name,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ci.movie_id) AS movie_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT t.title, ', ') AS movie_titles
    FROM 
        aka_name a
    LEFT JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        ranked_movies t ON ci.movie_id = t.movie_id
    GROUP BY 
        a.person_id, a.name
),
company_stats AS (
    SELECT 
        mc.movie_id,
        COUNT(DISTINCT cn.id) AS company_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT cn.name, ', ') AS company_names
    FROM 
        movie_companies mc
    JOIN 
        company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
    GROUP BY 
        mc.movie_id
),
movie_details AS (
    SELECT 
        rm.movie_id,
        rm.title,
        rm.production_year,
        ai.movie_count,
        ai.movie_titles,
        cs.company_count,
        cs.company_names
    FROM 
        ranked_movies rm
    LEFT JOIN 
        actor_info ai ON rm.movie_id = ai.movie_count
    LEFT JOIN 
        company_stats cs ON rm.movie_id = cs.movie_id
)
SELECT 
    md.title,
    md.production_year,
    COALESCE(md.movie_count, 0) AS actor_count,
    COALESCE(md.company_count, 0) AS company_count,
    CASE 
        WHEN md.movie_count IS NULL THEN 'No Actors'
        ELSE md.movie_titles 
    END AS actor_titles,
    CASE 
        WHEN md.company_count IS NULL THEN 'No Companies'
        ELSE md.company_names 
    END AS listed_companies
FROM 
    movie_details md
ORDER BY 
    md.production_year DESC, 
    md.title ASC

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."TITLE", "t4"."TITLE") AS "TITLE", "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", CASE WHEN "t4"."MOVIE_COUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."MOVIE_COUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ACTOR_COUNT", CASE WHEN "t6"."COMPANY_COUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t6"."COMPANY_COUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "COMPANY_COUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."MOVIE_COUNT" IS NULL THEN 'No Actors' ELSE "t4"."MOVIE_TITLES" END AS "ACTOR_TITLES", CASE WHEN "t6"."COMPANY_COUNT" IS NULL THEN 'No Companies' ELSE "t6"."COMPANY_NAMES" END AS "LISTED_COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."MOVIE_ID", "t1"."TITLE", "t1"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t1"."RAN", "t3"."PERSON_ID", "t3"."NAME", "t3"."MOVIE_COUNT", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLES"
FROM (SELECT "id" AS "MOVIE_ID", "title" AS "TITLE", "production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "production_year" ORDER BY "id") AS "RAN", CAST("id" AS BIGINT) AS "id"
FROM "aka_title") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "aka_name"."person_id" AS "PERSON_ID", "aka_name"."name" AS "NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."movie_id") AS "MOVIE_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "s1"."TITLE", ', ') AS "MOVIE_TITLES"
FROM "aka_name"
LEFT JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "s1"."MOVIE_ID"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name") AS "t3" ON "t1"."id" = "t3"."MOVIE_COUNT") AS "t4"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "movie_companies"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "company_name"."id") AS "COMPANY_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM "movie_companies"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
GROUP BY "movie_companies"."movie_id") AS "t6" ON "t4"."MOVIE_ID" = "t6"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."TITLE"

FROM "aka_title") AS "t2"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "aka_name"."person_id" AS "PERSON_ID", "aka_name"."name" AS "NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."movie_id") AS "MOVIE_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t3"."TITLE", ', ') AS "MOVIE_TITLES"
FROM "aka_name"
LEFT JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "id" AS "MOVIE_ID", "title" AS "TITLE", "production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "production_year" ORDER BY "id") AS "RAN"
FROM "aka_title") AS "t3" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t3"."MOVIE_ID"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name") AS "t5" ON "t2"."id" = "t5"."MOVIE_COUNT") AS "t6"

ORDER BY "t6"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t6"."TITLE"

LEFT JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "id" AS "MOVIE_ID", "title" AS "TITLE", "production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "production_year" ORDER BY "id") AS "RAN"
